{"confidence":{"mean_p":0.72,"min_p":0.42,"low_token_fraction":0.25,"token_count":12},"discord_id":"100000000000000008","id":"schlegel-4-4-u4","kind":"UtteranceAppended","session_id":"schlegel-4-4","status":"final","text":"Kommt, rührt euch! Frisch! Schon kräht der zweite Hahn, Die Morgenglocke läutet; ’s ist drei Uhr. Sieh nach dem Backwerk, Frau Angelika, Spar nichts daran!","ts":"2026-01-25T19:01:40Z"}
{"confidence":{"mean_p":0.94,"min_p":0.85,"low_token_fraction":0.05,"token_count":12},"discord_id":"100000000000000004","id":"schlegel-4-4-u5","kind":"UtteranceAppended","session_id":"schlegel-4-4","status":"final","text":"Topfgucker! Geht nur, geht! Macht euch zu Bett! – Gelt, ihr seid morgen krank, Wenn ihr die ganze Nacht nicht schlaft.","ts":"2026-01-25T19:01:50Z"}
{"confidence":{"mean_p":0.81,"min_p":0.51,"low_token_fraction":0.15,"token_count":12},"discord_id":"100000000000000008","id":"schlegel-4-4-u6","kind":"UtteranceAppended","session_id":"schlegel-4-4","status":"final","text":"Kein bißchen! Was? Ich hab’ um Kleiners wohl Die Nächte durchgewacht und war nie krank.","ts":"2026-01-25T19:02:00Z"}
{"confidence":{"mean_p":0.94,"min_p":0.85,"low_token_fraction":0.05,"token_count":12},"discord_id":"100000000000000009","id":"schlegel-4-4-u7","kind":"UtteranceAppended","session_id":"schlegel-4-4","status":"final","text":"Ja, ja! Ihr wart ein feiner Vogelsteller Zu eurer Zeit! Nun aber will ich euch Vor solchem Wachen schon bewachen.","ts":"2026-01-25T19:02:10Z"}
{"confidence":{"mean_p":0.94,"min_p":0.85,"low_token_fraction":0.05,"token_count":12},"discord_id":"100000000000000001","id":"schlegel-4-4-d8","kind":"UtteranceAppended","session_id":"schlegel-4-4","status":"final","text":"[Regie] (Gräfin und Wärterin ab.)","ts":"2026-01-25T19:02:20Z"}
{"confidence":{"mean_p":0.61,"min_p":0.28,"low_token_fraction":0.35,"token_count":12},"discord_id":"100000000000000008","id":"schlegel-4-4-u9","kind":"UtteranceAppended","session_id":"schlegel-4-4","status":"final","text":"O Ehestand, o Wehestand! – Nun, Kerl’, Was bringt ihr da?","ts":"2026-01-25T19:02:30Z"}
